    - memory_recall → classify-cast → gpt_oss: ~19s, $0.05
    - heartbeat → direct: 1.9s, $0.002

    Local daemon (src/):
    - CLI REPL, Claude Agent SDK, BizOps MCP, heartbeat scheduler, code executor
    - Fully functional but requires local machine running
    - Phase 1 complete, not actively needed now that edge kernel is live

